<span class="teaser-text">
</span>
Final guidelines on reopening of schools awaiting approval
</a> </p> </h3> <a href='#' class='person-name no-lnk'>Special Correspondent</a>
<span class="light-gray-color story-card-33-text hidden-xs">
Union School Education Secretary Anita Karwal convened a meeting of all State Education Secretaries on Monday to discuss the health and safety of students, hygiene measures in schools, and issues regarding online/digital learning in their States, according to Mr. Nishanks tweet. </span>
